  "description": "Use this skill when deploying an Experience Cloud site (formerly Community) between Salesforce orgs or sandboxes \u2014 including metadata ordering, ExperienceBundle enablement, post-deployment publishing, and change-set or SFDX-based migration. NOT for: LWC component development within Experience Builder, CMS content migration via Managed Content REST API, or Aura/LWC code authoring.",
  "file_location": "skills/devops/experience-cloud-deployment-admin",
  "id": "devops/experience-cloud-deployment-admin",
  "inputs": [
    "Source and target org types (sandbox, production, scratch org)",
    "Deployment mechanism in use: change set, Salesforce CLI (sf/sfdx), or Metadata API",
    "Site name and template type (LWR, Aura, Salesforce Tabs + Visualforce)",
    "Whether Enable Experience Bundle Metadata API is checked in both orgs",
    "Full list of metadata components the site depends on (Apex, profiles, permission sets, custom objects)"
  ],
  "name": "experience-cloud-deployment-admin",
